      <title>特朗普提名代理CDC首席莫纳雷斯（Monarez）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/white-house-plans-to-pick-acting-cdc-head-monarez-to-lead-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他正在提名疾病控制与预防中心代理主任苏珊·莫纳雷斯（Susan Monarez）担任该机构的常设负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/white-house-plans-to-pick-acting-cdc-head-monarez-to-lead-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 19:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，自动关税即将到来，戏弄了相互关税的休息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-says-auto-levies-coming-teases-reciprocal-tariff-breaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他将在未来几天内宣布对汽车进口的关税；并指出国家将从下周的“倒数”关税中获得休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-says-auto-levies-coming-teases-reciprocal-tariff-breaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 19:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉削减了政府工作周以口粮权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/venezuela-cuts-government-work-week-to-ration-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉正在将公职时间减少到一半，因为高温会影响水力发电厂的水坝，这一举动有可能在美国额外制裁的威胁下进一步减慢国家的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/venezuela-cuts-government-work-week-to-ration-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 18:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国在以色列罢工杀死员工后拉一些加沙工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/un-to-pull-some-gaza-workers-after-israeli-strike-kills-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国重新杀害了包括联合国工人在内的数百名平民杀害了数百名平民后，联合国正在减少在加沙的占地面积。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/un-to-pull-some-gaza-workers-after-israeli-strike-kills-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 18:41:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队的战争计划文本小组中包含的大西洋编辑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/atlantic-editor-included-in-trump-advisers-war-plan-text-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位大西洋的顶级编辑说，他被添加到了一个文本小组中，国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）分享了与其他美国顶级官员轰炸胡塞武装分子的详细计划，这是对政府反复发誓要限制泄漏的政府的非凡违反安全性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/atlantic-editor-included-in-trump-advisers-war-plan-text-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 18:12:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择阿丽娜·哈巴（Alina Habba）担任新泽西州临时律师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-picks-alina-habba-as-new-jersey-interim-us-attorney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他的前辩护律师阿丽娜·哈巴（Alina Habba）将成为她家乡新泽西州的临时律师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-picks-alina-habba-as-new-jersey-interim-us-attorney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言委内瑞拉石油买家的25％“次要”关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周一威胁要对委内瑞拉购买石油和天然气的任何国家对25％的关税，从而使他与拉丁美洲国家的移民争执，这一举动有可能冒着全球能源贸易的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称现代的美国扩张作为证明关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统庆祝了现代汽车公司（Hyundai Motor Co.）的计划，以在美国进行大量扩张，以证明其政府使用关税向外国制造商施加压力以创造美国就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国，俄罗斯团队在乌克兰举行“富有成效”演讲之后见面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/russia-and-us-teams-meet-after-ukraine-holds-productive-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和乌克兰队举行会谈后，美国和俄罗斯官员每天在沙特阿拉伯见面约12个小时，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统在战争中取得了停火的进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/russia-and-us-teams-meet-after-ukraine-holds-productive-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 07:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>十亿美元的美国对中国船只的征税风险“贸易启示录”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/trump-s-tariffs-billion-dollar-levies-on-chinese-ships-risk-trade-apocalypse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[批评家将在周一举行的听证会上，与特朗普的关税相比，针对商业船只的举动可能更具破坏性。。]]></description>
